Alphah/Nightstrike::

Alphah arrived first to Medical Bay and said "Quickly put him on the 
table..."

Nightstrike continued moaning as if something was hurting him "I 
can't manage it..."he said""

"Why did you said that, what's going on???" asked Alphah"Epyon, we 
must sedate him again... Hold him!!!"

Replied Alphah  while she tried to find a gun with sleep-darts.
